! Coupled VIE ORIENT command: a single tagged command must update the lens-draw
! orientation AND its coupled elevation/azimuth in one shot, order-independent.
!   ORIENT <YZ|XZ|XY|ORTHO> [ELEV <deg>] [AZI <deg>]
! ELEV/AZI are children of the orientation owner: the owner's regenerated command
! carries them (generatePlotCommand skips the children), so a replot round-trips.
! Args arrive uppercased, so ORTHO must resolve regardless of typed case.
RES osdtriplet
VIE
ORIENT ORTHO ELEV 37.3 AZI 48.3
NUMRAYS 9
GO
